Date: 1995-03-07

Title: Bosonization of World-Sheet Fermions in Minkowski Space-Time

Authors: A. Pasquinucci and K. Roland

Comments: 1+9 pages, TeX macros included

Journal-ref: Phys. Lett. B351 (1995) 131

We propose a way of bosonizing free world-sheet fermions for $4$-dimensionalheterotic string theory formulated in Minkowski space-time. We discuss thedifferences as compared to the standard bosonization performed in Euclideanspace-time.